# 🏦 Simple ATM System (Python)

A basic command-line ATM simulation built using Python. Users can check their balance, deposit money, withdraw money, and exit the program through a simple menu-driven interface.

---

## 📌 Features

- 💰 Check account balance
- ➕ Deposit money
- ➖ Withdraw money
- 🚫 Prevents withdrawal if balance is insufficient
- 🔄 Menu-driven program using a loop
- ❌ Exit option

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- Python 3

